{"title":"农村大字报","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":7,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"农村大字报"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带头就是党支书"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家来看大家听，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上游干部大家评；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我社干部决心大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带头就是党支书。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"支部书记覃肇忠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"执行决议利如风；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用尽千方和百计，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领导工作有大功。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肇忠同志当好家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚持集体压自发；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全部收回私人开荒地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"消灭资本主义有办法。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（广西宜山县?达农业社）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自满不得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八队生产顶呱呱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人看见称赞他。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早造生产做得好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可惜晚造备耕积肥差。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主要原因是自满，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经常都说胜人家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"若不力争上游起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将来生产就会垮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（广东怀集县诗洞乡六福社）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要泄气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大字报上点了名，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人心里实在不高兴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他说“辛辛苦苦搞工作，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在还要挨批评，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以后百事我不理，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任你将我去点名。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劝声同志莫生气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"批评不是整垮你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了缺点能改正，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家对你更欢迎；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勤劳生产工作好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人定会把你称。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（广东云浮县料洞乡农业社）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说恼不恼？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是宝中宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"名字安得好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人都爱我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"得我如得宝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惟有社领导，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"待我如粪草，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老鼠来吃我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃饱唱着跑；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虫儿来吃我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我真受不了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家来评评，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说恼不恼？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（广西平乐县妙口农业社）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}